com.mlab.gpx.api
Interface GpxDocument

All Known Implementing Classes:
GpxDocumentImpl
public interface GpxDocument

Interface for GpxDocuments. A GpxDocument has one Metadata element, a List of WayPoint's, a List of Route's, a List of Tracks and one Extensions element.
It has a method to get a java DomDocument and methods to add, remove or get WayPoints, Routes and Tracks

shiguera
